  <body>

    <div class="container">

      <div class="picture">
        <div>
          <img style="width: 100%" src="<%= asset_path("ianne.jpg") %>" alt="ianne">
        </div>

        <div>
          <img style="width: 100%" src="<%= asset_path("twins.jpeg") %>" alt="twins">
        </div>

        <div>
          <img style="width: 100%" src="<%= asset_path("voltaire.jpg") %>" alt="voltaire">
        </div>

        <div>
          <img style="width: 100%" src="<%= asset_path("dorothytoto.jpg") %>" alt="dorothytoto">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <section class="intro">
           <h1>Anne & Ian's</h1>
           <h2>Halloween Wedding Pizza Dance Party!</h2>

           <a class="button" href="#events">PARTY</a>
           <a class="button" href="#RSVP">RSVP</a>
           <a class="button" href="#story">STORY</a>
           <a class="button" href="#lodging">LODGING</a>
        </section><!-- #intro -->

        <section class="story">
          <a id="story">
           <h2>The story goes...</h2>

           <p>Once upon a time, there was this company called Knewton. They needed a video guy to make online courses or something.
           They hired this joker named Ian and Ian created this really good GMAT course. Anne, a retired banker,
           confused about her purpose in life decided to apply to business school and took Knewton's GMAT course that Ian made.
           Obviously she did really well.</p>
           <p> After she graduated she moved to the big apple
           in search of her dream job, which turned out to be an Adaptive Instruction Analyst at Knewton. Ian still happened
           to be at Knewton when Anne joined and he admired her from afar, knowing that a babe like Anne would never be interested
           in a turd like him.</p>
           <p> Fast forward a year or so and Ian has left Knewton. Anne is desperate for love and turns to technology to help.
           One nigh, in a drunken stupor, Anne swipes right on a picture of some rando dude, not knowing that it's the ogre, Ian
         who had been admiring her from afar.</p>
         <p> They end up dating and then they go on this amazing trip to all kinds of places like Tokyo, Ho Chi Minh and Falls Church, Virginia.
           And then one day Anne proposes.</p>
        </section><!-- #story -->

        <section class="events">
          <a id="events">
           <h2>Wait...so now what?</h2>

           <p>So we did the whole ceremony, white dress, golden tux thing and we don't really want to have a fancy sit-down reception, so instead we are throwing a HALLOWEEN-THEMED PIZZA DANCE PARTY.</p>

           <h3>When?</h3>
            <p>6:30pm on Saturday, November 5th, 2017</p>

            <h2>Where?</h2>
            <p><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/230+Bogart+St,+Brooklyn,+NY+11206/@40.7116674,-73.9376569,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89c25eab2ede40bb:0x2b152bd7465088f1!8m2!3d40.7116634!4d-73.9354629" target="_blank">230 Bogart St, Brooklyn, NY 11206</a></p>

            <h2>What should I wear?</h2>
            <p>This part is very important so read carefully.</p>

            <h2>Anything else?</h2>
            <p>Join us for coffee and doughnuts with us in <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Msgr.+McGolrick+Park/@40.7244435,-73.9433581,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x502c61b7a733459e!8m2!3d40.7244435!4d-73.9433581?sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwidiarxzoPTAhWJ8oMKHdTrCK8Q_BIIeTAO" target="_blank">McGolrick Park</a> on Sunday, November 6th (NYC Marathon Day) at 11:00am</p>
        </section><!-- #events -->

        <section class="rsvp">
          <a id="RSVP">

          <iframe src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdToTqrxCM3vdsDMfn8KojwhRkwBddejF5LrlICBv3LM_Lhcw/viewform?embedded=true#start=embed" width=100% height="1500" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" font-family="Open-Sans"></iframe>
        </section><!-- #rsvp -->

        <section class="lodging">
          <a id="lodging">
          <p>If you are coming from out of town, here are some nice places to stay:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="http://www.henrynormanhotel.com/" target="_blank">Henry Norman Hotel</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://wythehotel.com/" target="_blank">Wythe Hotel</a></li>
            <li><a href="http://www.franklinguesthouse.com/" target="_blank">Franklin Guesthouse</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.airbnb.com/s/Greenpoint--Brooklyn--NY--United-States?guests=2&adults=2&children=0&infants=0&checkin=09%2F29%2F2017&checkout=10%2F01%2F2017&ss_id=piqdzc0a&ss_preload=true&source=bb&page=1&s_tag=Xtw7i7cv&allow_override%5B%5D=" target="_blank">Airbnb</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section><!-- #lodging -->
      </div><!-- #content -->

      <div class="clear"></div>

    </div><!-- #container -->

    <script type="text/javascript" src="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/jquery.slick/1.6.0/slick.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      $(document).ready(function(){
        $('.picture').slick({
          slidesToShow: 1,
          slidesToScroll: 1,
          autoplay: true,
          fade: true,
          autoplaySpeed: 3000,
          dots: false,
          arrows: false
        });
      });
    </script>

  </body>
</html>
